description: One section of the spectacular East Coast Trail - from Cape Spear to Maddox Cove
directions: At Cape Spear, park at the lighthouse and head south along the shore.  The official trail head starts 500m south of the upper lighthouse.At Maddox Cove, park on the side of Old Maddox Cove Rd, just off the main Maddox Cove Road.  The trail starts 200 m up Shore Lane.
title: East Coast Trail - Cape Spear Path
